<div class="nbunit" id="25May1937"><font color="red">25 May 1937</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Alfred Bergan): Mr Devin&apos;s song was &lsquo;O boys, keep away from the girls I say&rsquo; &hellip; He comes into Ulysses under the name of &lsquo;Mr Power&rsquo; &hellip; The Lord knows whether you will be able to pick the Kersse-McCann story out of my crazy tale. It was a great story of my father&apos;s </div>
